    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 50-53.</p><p>World Strike</p><p>When you reach 20th level, you learn to channel your martial prowess into a singular, ki-augmented strike. You can use your action and expend 1 Legendary Point to make an unarmed attack or melee weapon attack against a creature within range. This attack deals 4d8 x</p><p>Focus Points</p><p>Martial</p><p>Unarmored</p><p>Arts</p><p>Movement</p><p>Points</p><p>5 Soul damage to that target. This attack does not benefit from any bonus to its damage. On a critical hit, you do not multiply the damage dice by 2, but instead deal 6d8 x 5 Soul damage. You cannot use your Stunning Strike on this attack.</p><p>On a hit, you can expend 8 Focus points to force the target to make a DC 30 Constitution saving throw. On a failure, the target is stunned until the end of its next turn.</p></div>",
